an>3388 浏览\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <a href=\"https://www.woshipm.com/it/5781366.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"img-link\" title=\"抖音、美团、滴滴的七年之痒\"><img class=\"cover\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251023161621_9fff36\" alt=\"抖音、美团、滴滴的七年之痒\"></a>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"relate-text__item\">\n        <div class=\"content\">\n         <div class=\"title\">\n          <a href=\"https://www.woshipm.com/pd/5934758.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"为什么你的SCRM用不起来？\">为什么你的SCRM用不起来？</a>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"meta\">\n          11-07<span class=\"dot\"></span>3200 浏览\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <a href=\"https://www.woshipm.com/pd/5934758.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"img-link\" title=\"为什么你的SCRM用不起来？\"><img class=\"cover\" src=\"https://image.yunyingpai.com/wp/2023/11/cYBiFxJrrIlONYXSbQIe.jpg!/both/120x80\" alt=\"为什么你的SCRM用不起来？\"></a>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"u-backgroundColorWhite comments-area u-shadowed u-rounded\">\n      <div class=\"comment-list-header\">\n       <span class=\"title\">评论</span>\n      </div>\n      <div id=\"respond\" class=\"respond respond-6187399\" role=\"form\">\n       <form action=\"https://www.woshipm.com/wp-comments-post.php\" method=\"post\" id=\"commentform\" data-post=\"6187399\" class=\"comment-form u-clearfix\">\n        <div class=\"textarea--unlogin\" @click=\"showLoginForm\">评论请登录</div>\n        <div class=\"comment-form-bottom u-clearfix\">\n         <input class=\"comment-submit u-floatRight\" type=\"submit\" value=\"发布\" @click=\"showLoginForm\" data-dts-event-location=\"comment\" data-dts-event-info=\"{&quot;article_id&quot;:6187399}\">\n        </div>\n       </form>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"commentshow\">\n       <ol class=\"comment-list\">\n        <li class=\"comment byuser comment-author-18565100596 even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-588549\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Comment\" itemscope itemprop=\"comment\">\n         <div id=\"comment-588549\" class=\"comment-block\">\n          <div class=\"comment-avatar\">\n           <a href=\"https://www.woshipm.com/u/1616222\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://static.woshipm.com/passport_avatar_wx_20250228174158_4826.jpg?imageView2/1/w/80/h/80/q/100\" alt=\"\" height=\"40\" width=\"40\" class=\"avatar\"></a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"comment-section\">\n           <div class=\"comment-info\">\n            <div class=\"comment-meta\">\n             <div class=\"comment-author\" itemprop=\"author\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.woshipm.com/u/1616222\" target=\"_blank\">棠棠呆球</a>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"comment-content\" itemprop=\"description\">\n            <p>其实我觉得AI在一定程度上提高工作上的效率，如果用对正途，AI何尝不是帮手。</p>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"comment-bottom\">\n            <span class=\"comment-time\" itemprop=\"datePublished\" datetime=\"2025-03-07T16:37:20+08:00\">最近</span> <span class=\"comment-reply\">来自广东</span> <span @click=\"moveForm\" data-id=\"588549\" class=\"comment-reply\">回复</span> <span class=\"js-report-content\" @click=\"showReport(588549)\"> <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b0504319-e7a9-4ea7-3f46-52f9506dd600/public\" width=\"16\"> </span>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </li>\n        <!-- #comment-## -->\n        <li class=\"comment byuser comment-author-18318528506 odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-588493\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Comment\" itemscope itemprop=\"comment\">\n         <div id=\"comment-588493\" class=\"comment-block\">\n          <div class=\"comment-avatar\">\n           <a href=\"https://www.woshipm.com/u/1616233\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://static.woshipm.com/woshipm_def_head_2022_1.jpg?imageView2/1/w/80/h/80/q/100\" alt=\"\" height=\"40\" width=\"40\" class=\"avatar\"></a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"comment-section\">\n           <div class=\"comment-info\">\n            <div class=\"comment-meta\">\n             <div class=\"comment-author\" itemprop=\"author\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.woshipm.com/u/1616233\" target=\"_blank\">wen</a>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"comment-content\" itemprop=\"description\">\n            <p>AI在广告创意制作中的应用确实带来了巨大的变革，不仅提升了效率，还降低了成本。然而，AI的局限性在于缺乏真正的创新和情感共鸣，这仍然是人类创作者的独特优势。未来，广告行业将更加依赖人机协作，AI负责高效生成，人类则专注于创意和情感表达。</p>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"comment-bottom\">\n            <span class=\"comment-time\" itemprop=\"datePublished\" datetime=\"2025-03-05T14:00:44+08:00\">最近</span> <span class=\"comment-reply\">来自海南</span> <span @click=\"moveForm\" data-id=\"588493\" class=\"comment-reply\">回复</span> <span class=\"js-report-content\" @click=\"showReport(588493)\"> <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b0504319-e7a9-4ea7-3f46-52f9506dd600/public\" width=\"16\"> </span>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </li>\n        <!-- #comment-## -->\n       </ol>\n       <nav class=\"commentnav\" data-fuck=\"6187399\"></nav>\n      </div>\n      <comment-report :show.sync=\"reportVisivle\" :id=\"reportComment\"></comment-report>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"relatedPosts u-backgroundColorWhite u-rounded u-marginTop20 u-shadowed\">\n      <nav class=\"stream-video--title\">\n       <span class=\"title\">为你推荐</span>\n      </nav>\n      <div class=\"relatedPosts--list\" data-dts-event-location=\"interested_items\">\n       <div class=\"relatedPosts--half\">\n        <ul class=\"relatedPosts--group\" data-dts-event-location=\"interested_items\">\n         <li class=\"relatedPosts--item__small\">\n          <div class=\"img\">\n           <a href=\"https://www.woshipm.com/operate/5959475.html\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251023161621_61088f\" width=\"130\" height=\"88\" alt=\"社区营造万字总结，这